{{Taxobox | image = Psilocybe muliercula 105891.jpg | image_width = 240px | image_caption = ''Psilocybe angustipleurocystidiata'' | regnum = [[Fungi]] | divisio = [[Basidiomycota]] | classis = [[Agaricomycetes]] | ordo = [[Agaricales]] | familia = [[Hymenogastraceae]] | genus = ''[[Psilocybe]]'' | species = '''''P. angustipleurocystidiata''''' | binomial = ''Psilocybe angustipleurocystidiata'' | binomial_authority = [[Gastón Guzmán|Guzmán]] (1983) | synonyms = }}
'''''Psilocybe angustipleurocystidiata''''' is a Mexican species of [[entheogenic]] [[mushroom]] in the family [[Hymenogastraceae]]. It contains the compounds [[psilocybin]] and [[psilocin]].
This mushroom was first [[species description|described]] by [[Mexico|Mexican]] [[mycologist]] [[Gaston Guzman]].<ref name="Guzmán 1983"/> ''Psilocybe angustipleurocystidiata'' has been found in the [[state of Mexico]], [[Morelos]] and [[Veracruz, Veracruz|Vera Cruz]], where it is common in [[subtropical]] ''[[Pinus]]'' and ''[[Alnus]]'' forests at elevations between {{convert|1800|and|2400|m|ft}}.
''Psilocybe angustipleurocystidiata'' is in the [[section (botany)|section]] ''Zapotecorum'' of the genus ''[[Psilocybe]]'', other members of this section include ''[[Psilocybe muliercula]]'', ''[[Psilocybe aucklandii]]'', ''[[Psilocybe collybioides]]'', ''[[Psilocybe graveolens]]'', ''[[Psilocybe kumaenorum]]'', ''[[Psilocybe zapotecorum]]'', ''[[Psilocybe pintonii]]'', ''[[Psilocybe subcaerulipes]]'', ''[[Psilocybe moseri]]'', ''[[Psilocybe zapotecoantillarum]]'', ''[[Psilocybe zapotecocaribaea]]'', and ''[[Psilocybe antioquiensis]]''.<ref name="Guzman2012">{{cite journal |last=Guzmán |first=Gastón |authorlink=Gastón Guzmán |title= New Taxonomical and Ethnomycological Observations on Psilocybe S.S. From Mexico, Africa and Spain |journal=Acta Botanica Mexicana |year=2012 |volume=100 |pages=79–106 |url=http://dialnet.unirioja.es/descarga/articulo/3988750.pdf}}</ref><ref name="Ramirez-Cruz2013">{{cite journal |last1=Ramírez-Cruz |first1=Virginia |last2=Guzmán |first2=Gastón |last3= Villalobos-Arámbula |first3=Alma Rosa |last4=Rodríguez |first4=Aarón |last5=Matheny |first5=Brandon |last6= Sánchez-García |first6=Marisol |last7=Guzmán-Dávalos |first7=Laura |title=Phylogenetic inference and trait evolution of the psychedelic mushroom genus ''Psilocybe'' sensu lato (Agaricales)|journal=Botany |year=2013 |volume=91 |pages=573–591 |url=http://www.nrcresearchpress.com/doi/abs/10.1139/cjb-2013-0070#.VH_zGTHF9Vs |doi=10.1139/cjb-2013-0070}}</ref>
